msgid "Heterotrait-Monotrait Ratio"
msgstr ""

msgid "Heterotrait-Monotrait (HTMT) ratio of correlations for assessing discriminant validity. HTMT values below 0.85 (conservative) or 0.90 (liberal) suggest that constructs are empirically distinct from each other."
msgstr ""

msgid "Mardia's Coefficients"
